generate locale data
	edit /etc/locale.gen      uncomment EN_US utf_8 line
	sudo locale-gen


fonts: needed nerdfonts i think for terminal. toff2 or something variant
	for waybar.


kanata:
stow systemd      (stow -nv systemd     to see what it will do beforehand)
	for ~/dotfiles/systemd/.config/systemd/user/kanata.service

systemctl --user daemon-reload       for after changing location of some service file
systemctl --user enable --now kanata.service
